{"tid":1543443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成萬人入機場塞都多鳩餘！","createTime":"2019-09-05T07:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T09:29:49.000Z","uid":298978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4442442b46bccdcf1a2577eae7e6b653c818b235","tid":1543443,"uid":298978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:38:03.000Z","msg":"上次成萬人迫入去，狗隻一出又成萬人行返出黎！喂！行成左8公里呀！<br />\n而家係時候要出<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大絕！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2公里車龍連</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2公里係咩概念？即係100架車車龍，又即係彌敦道旺角塞到尖沙咀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">即刻同我搵100架車出黎！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GxjAWki.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGxjAWki.jpg&h=0ec43d9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n準時1pm 到達<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">青嶼幹線觀景台</span></span>然後打圈，咁就可以塞哂港九新界入機場既車！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係對唔住........<br />\n其實我只係步兵，我報左名參加彩虹戰衣機場百萬行...各位車手要加油，到時見...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JkZEDAx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJkZEDAx.jpg&h=7f54c134&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uW6C9Hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuW6C9Hd.jpg&h=5e38127f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jXzpPHe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjXzpPHe.jpg&h=2cd7b798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQoRuHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQoRuHg.jpg&h=73b9404c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c78e80ad002d2dd991ea87ad73a756948810957","tid":1543443,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:38:12.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bd236f7e053267336105013eee071b80504f62a","tid":1543443,"uid":8812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"88dcb7b81cf96c3f1cb541e3b8f71c95445adee0","tid":1543443,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">唔塞機場 啲空管主任同crew咪係東涌搭到車返工囉弱智</span>"},{"pid":"aaf0c8d41c67028f32367a62b2ac2b61ffe5f156","tid":1543443,"uid":283587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"弱弱一問，機場啲貨運，我指啲貨車係經什麼路入返市區？"},{"pid":"09b853a648ee85367ce07b12893374b64cf63947","tid":1543443,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:02:39.000Z","msg":"今朝兜過車手攻略，發覺得塞唔到入機場嘅路"},{"pid":"773c451234c478e6cd25f20586358c892daf52aa","tid":1543443,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05